## 9. POST Requests & req.body

To receive data from frontend (forms, React apps etc.):

```js
// MUST add this middleware to read JSON body
app.use(express.json())

app.post('/register', (req, res) => {
  console.log(req.body) // { name: "Rahul", email: "rahul@gmail.com" }
  res.json({ message: "User registered!" })
})
```

Without `app.use(express.json())`, `req.body` will be `undefined`!

