## 15. The Three Ways Data Reaches Your Server

```
req.body    → POST data (form submissions, login, register)
req.params  → route parameters (/users/:id)
req.query   → query strings (/users?city=jaipur)
```

Real world examples:
```
Click on a product     → /products/:id        → req.params
Search by category     → /products?cat=shoes  → req.query
Submit signup form     → POST /register       → req.body
```

